FBIS3-5844 "dreas048__a94007" FBIS-EAS-94-048-A Document Type:Daily Report 11 March 1994 ANNEX Japan DA Director Aichi Plans To Visit U.S. OW1103113594 Tokyo MAINICHI SHIMBUN in Japanese 11 Mar 94 Morning Edition p 3 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW1103113594 Tokyo MAINICHI SHIMBUN Language: Japanese Article Type:BFN [Text] Kazuo Aichi, director general of the Defense Agency [DA], met with Larson, commander of the U.S. Pacific Command, at the Defense Agency on 10 March. During the meeting, he made clear that he intends to visit the United States during the holiday season that begins at the end of April. He is expected to hold his first Japan-U.S. defense summit meeting with U.S. Defense Secretary Perry. During the meeting, Commander Larson said he will retire in early May.
